-- Geithner Promises to Look Into Swiss Bank Talks, Widmer Says
-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 2012-01-28T12:59:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-28/geithner-promises-to-look-into-swiss-bank-talks-widmer-says.html
U.S. Treasury Secretary  Timothy Geithner  promised to personally monitor talks with  Switzerland 
over undeclared bank accounts Swiss Finance Minister Eveline Widmer-Schlumpf said in an interview with told Swiss television
station SF.  The minister said she had a “very good, open” discussion
with Geithner and thinks he got the message that Switzerland
wants to find a solution as quickly as possible, according to
the interview posted on SF website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elena Logutenkova in Zurich at 
